snippet.title: Over a Pipe
snippet.description: Hey everyone!!! Welcome to my channel where I like to discuss tobacco related and not related topics Over a Pipe. This is a place where I will share my opinion and information gathered from resources all over. This is for fun and enjoyment. We are here to commune and support one another the best way we can. I will also notify you if you like, share, subscribe and hit the notification bell of rare tobaccos when they come in stock. Rare Tobaccos such as Esoterica: Penzance, Stonehaven, and the like. I will also let you know when Pelican, Balkan Sobranie, and J.F. Germain tobaccos come in stock. So sit back and enjoy some of my videos....Over a Pipe.
